title: The Original Fleetwood Mac: The Early Years [1967-1970] DVD5
description: The Original Fleetwood Mac: The Early Years [1967-1970] DVD5 This is the probably the only video (story) recording during Peter Green's playing days with Fleetwood Mac. This video follows the band in their Bitish blues heyday. This is long before the the pop rock band that most people are familiar with. The music and the video are raw and capture the time in which they were made.
